This documentation describes Event Alerts for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF).

## <a id='overview'></a>Overview

PCF Event Alerts is a service that sends event alerts as email and Slace notifications.

## <a id='features'></a>Key Features

The Event Alerts service enables you to notify users about Healthwatch alerts:

* Send notifications by email to specific users and to distribution lists.
* Send notifications to Slack channels.

